In frame- @daughterearthofficial 

Does your undereye look ashy even after applying concealer? or do you find it difficult to blend your concealer then here is a perfect concealer from @daughterearthofficial which helps you to conceal your dark circle in no time.

My personal experience 
@daughterearthofficial concealer has Creamy formula, Easy to blend, covers my dark circles like magic and gives flawless look.

Tips- Always colour correct if you have intense dark circles with orange corrector and then apply concealer which matches your skin tone.

Note- do not apply lighter concealer as it will make your undereye or pigmentation look ashy.
